An idea that turned my passion project into purpose and performance was to create authentic silver jewelry. Simplicity , history , nature , minimalism , comfort and story have defined our design ethos. 

As we grow in numbers and scale up , there are processes and practices that we want to stay honest and consistent with. 

When we made our kudi , the earring that you see in this video. We were clear to create it in this particular way and not create a mould and mass manufacture it. This kudi and the kudi created with a mould are a world of a difference. And I am glad that as I write this post we have shipped more than 50000 of these earrings to every corner of the world. 

While we believe in exploring every technique to create silver jewelry , we at Aadyaa still make a large of our jewelry the traditional way. 

Today we start with a new journey on our social media handles to share what it takes to create , innovate , upgrade. It is also a reminder to all of us at Aadyaa. This is what defines us. 

Here is making of kudi ! Detailed video will be out real soon ! Hope you like this series.
